title: Bertie Plays the Blues
author: McCall Smith, Alexander
snippet: Matthew couldn't, she decided: he was far too tired. If he decided to go off he would probably reach only as far as India Street or Ainslie Place before he dropped from exhaustion – that would be no good for another woman. Other women tended to have greater expectations of the men they seduced away from their proper station.
